        {
            "title": "非農報告今晚揭曉，美元跌破101大關！黃金、比特幣受鴿派信號提振",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong>周四，7月2日，聯儲局新主席Warsh上任後首份非農就業報告將於香港時間今晚20：30揭曉，市場預計6月非農就業人數預計新增11.3萬，較5月17.2萬大幅回落；失業率預計持平於4.3%。美股開市前，美股指期貨升跌不一，納指100期貨跌200點，跌幅達0.74%，道指30期貨升0.01%，標普500期貨跌0.22%。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/2kv5I2H20TB_mtHWvQplsQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://d55-invdn-com.investing.com/content/069fb5dabc6b3215774149b630e57fe8.png\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">沃什鴿派發言提振貴金屬行情，XAU/USD反彈升1%重返4000美元，白銀升至59美元上方。倫敦布倫特原油期貨跌至71.18美元；WTI原油現報68.2美元。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-93bfc2eb-1c7a-3644-82cd-ce7a5d0c33d3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/pW4c002Jg3jDY58Mk2HD3g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://d55-invdn-com.investing.com/content/8da3ce5af28dbbc81a069fb85e0b94f0.png\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聯儲局鴿派信號打壓美元，美元指數直線回落跌0.43%，跌破101大關。 聯儲局主席沃什在歐央行論壇上明確表示，聯儲局將放棄利率前瞻指引，未來決策完全依賴即時經濟數據。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/uRqXvNmRNNpcB415TtMLkg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://d55-invdn-com.investing.com/content/246989363abaff4b304d08ef1161a021.png\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">比特幣 (BitfinexUSD)反彈升超2%，重回6萬美元上方。Coinglass數據顯示，最近24小時，加密貨幣市場超12萬人爆倉，爆倉金額達4.47億美元。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Ziu3IjEDkAgebndHvFX9yA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://d55-invdn-com.investing.com/content/3f25466b745ae6fc1d8df3c0893b6a59.png\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><blockquote class=\"border-pebble mx-5 my-7.5 border-l-2 pl-5 italic\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><strong><u><span>今次真系抵到爆！InvestingPro限时6折，全年最低价错过唔再有！</span></u></strong><strong><span><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"即刻點擊訂閱\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:即刻點擊訂閱;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.investing.com/pro/pricing?utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_campaign=yahoo-hk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><em><span>即刻點擊訂閱</span></em></a></span></strong><strong><u><span>！</span></u></strong></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w